flowchart TD
    S1[Fetch Pending + Partially Fulfilled Requests] --> S2[Sort by Urgency and Required Volume]
    S2 --> S3[Pick One Request]
    S3 --> S4[Find Compatible Bags via COMPATIBILITY_MATRIX]
    S4 --> S5[Sort Candidate Bags by Preference and Expiry FIFO]
    S5 --> S6{Need Fully Satisfied?}
    S6 -->|No| S7[Take min Needed vs Bag Volume]
    S7 --> S8[Insert FULFILLMENT_LOG]
    S8 --> S9[Update BLOOD_BAG current_volume_ml]
    S9 --> S10[DB Triggers Update Request Status and Audit]
    S10 --> S6
    S6 -->|Yes| S11[Move to Next Request]
    S11 --> S12{More Requests?}
    S12 -->|Yes| S3
    S12 -->|No| S13[Commit Transaction and Return Summary]
